What is a flutter?
A tool that allows you to build native cross-platforms apps with one programming language and codebase.

Dart?
Programming language developed by google
Object-oriented and strongly typed
Syntax is like a mixture of javascript,c#,java
Focused on frontend user interface development

command for open a ios simulator (Mac OS)
open -a Simulator
-Setting in simulator's Haradware -> Device -> IOS11.3-> iPhone8

If you want to set device scale in Mac OS
- set the device scale under the Window > Scale menu in the simulator
- Starting the app - flutter run

